A SDK for creating blockchains more easily
text: Currently, the number of L1 and L2 blockchains is constantly increasing, but at the same time it's extremely complex to create a new blockchain from scratch. Wouldn't it be possible to consider a framework in the form of an SDK, for example, that offers all the necessary tools for creators of new blockchains? It could be similar to how React drastically simplified front-end development a few years ago.
